Articles.Content: Since you only have 4MB RAM you're most likely simply running out of memory.
you mean 4GB but it shows i still have memory left

1 hour ago, Trem Fantasma said:

you mean 4GB but it shows i still have memory left

True, however what is being shown by your logs is that you are experiencing a memory access violation which is casued by insufficient physical memory in this case

In addition to this you are running KSP off of your desktop which is prone to leaving you open to crashes as win-doh's doesn't like to give permissions to non Microsoft programs to access system folders and the files contained within

Might I suggest reducing the amount of mods you are running and move your KSP install to some other non-system directory 

Edited April 5, 2017 by DoctorDavinci
